Sherman Yan

## Design Document ##

- Assignment 5 - P5.4 -

- Inputs

    A string

- Processing

    Return the middle character in a string

- Parameters and Return

    Parameter: string
    Return: middle character(s)

- Pseudocode

Length = length of string
middleIndex = floor of  Length of string / 2
If length % 2 == 0
Return string at middle index  - 1 + string at middle index
Else
Return string at middle index

- Code

def middle(word):
    length = len(word)

    middle_index = length // 2

    if length % 2 == 0:
        return str(word[middle_index - 1] + word[middle_index])
    else:
        return str(word[middle_index])





